  "3070420": {
    "name": "武林霸图",
    "steam_appid": 3070420,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合了回合制战术、实时基地管理与大战略。领导您的门派、训练弟子、缔结同盟，征服整个武林——在这里，每一次攻击的结果，包含战利品，都完全确定。再也没有95%命中率的失手：胜利由策略铸就，而非运气。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造，训练，战斗，称霸武林。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回合制战术战斗与实时基地管理和角色成长相结合，一切都为您的宏大战略服务。领导您的武侠门派，建造据点，打造武器，训练弟子，扩张领土，结交盟友，并参与深度战术战斗，称霸武林。无随机性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>培养弟子，塑造传奇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >培养您的弟子成为武林传奇，或训练他们掌握维持门派繁荣所需的实用技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/f26abfb99e0b00f8c8d181a1543536fa.poster.avif?t=1760257969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/f26abfb99e0b00f8c8d181a1543536fa.webm?t=1760257969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/f26abfb99e0b00f8c8d181a1543536fa.mp4?t=1760257969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>锻造与修炼：</strong> 精通六大类武学：拳脚、刀剑、长柄、暗器、轻功和内功。每一类都包含数十种独特招式，真正的天才可以全部掌握。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>招募与培养：</strong> 从众多独特的弟子中进行探查和招募。弟子的天赋受其出身影响，您必须因材施教。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理您的门派：</strong> 通过向弟子收取学费和向雇佣工人支付工资来管理门派的经济。一名全职武者需要大量的支持，因此建立一个繁荣的门派是您成功的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>实时管理您的门派</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实时建造和设计您的门派，以优化效率、防御和战略发展。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/38bc2d39130a3f120bef54471f6b6db0.poster.avif?t=1760257969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/38bc2d39130a3f120bef54471f6b6db0.webm?t=1760257969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/38bc2d39130a3f120bef54471f6b6db0.mp4?t=1760257969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义基地建设：</strong> 设计您的基地以优化生产和训练，将其转变为商业中心或武学圣地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战略布局：</strong> 布置您的建筑以获得防御优势，并在战斗中最大限度地减少损失。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生生不息的经济：</strong> 与商人交易并管理您的员工以创造财富，为关键职位雇佣管事，并建立一个繁荣的门派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的建筑：</strong> 建造、升级和拆除各种建筑，从练功房、锻造坊到用于研发新武学的藏经阁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无随机性的回合制战术战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与战术性回合制战斗，战略定位和预先规划将决定战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/21e5de1feb12a0cd0fc9afbbad567e91.poster.avif?t=1760257969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/21e5de1feb12a0cd0fc9afbbad567e91.webm?t=1760257969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/21e5de1feb12a0cd0fc9afbbad567e91.mp4?t=1760257969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>纯粹策略：</strong> 成功取决于周密的计划——没有随机性可以拯救或毁灭您。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>行动前预知结果：</strong> 在您确认攻击前即可看到结果，让您能够精确地计划每一步行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>永久死亡：</strong> 如果在战斗中未能救下一名弟子，他们将永远消失。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的门派：</strong> 每个武林门派都专注于不同的风格，从而产生截然不同的战斗策略和游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态战场：</strong> 利用3D战场中多样的地形和可破坏的环境来获得优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义您的武库：</strong> 搜刮、回收和自定义各种武器装备，为每场战斗找到完美的组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>征服或存续</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过五种不同的胜利条件选择您自己的荣耀之路，并通过与世界的互动塑造您门派的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/4e90aba0d760db0cfa3cca3384192688.poster.avif?t=1760257969\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/4e90aba0d760db0cfa3cca3384192688.webm?t=1760257969\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070420/extras/4e90aba0d760db0cfa3cca3384192688.mp4?t=1760257969\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>五种胜利之道：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独霸江湖</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >富可敌国</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天下第一</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武林盟主</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至高武学</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个鲜活的世界：</strong> 您门派的存亡取决于您与各国帝王、藩镇、绿林、义军、平民以及其他武林同道的互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恶名昭彰或声名显赫：</strong> 抢劫、交易或保护路过的商队。您的门派可以因其善行而闻名江湖，或因其恶行而臭名昭著，这两种选择都将对世界产生巨大影响。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隐士之路：</strong> 名望并非您唯一的选择。您可以保持门派的默默无闻，通过远离世事纷扰而生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚔️ 每位弟子。每场战斗。每个选择。您的门派故事将由您亲自谱写。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
